## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Task selection for demo**: I plan to have two predefined agent tasks — one that completes normally (TASK-001) and one that triggers the unauthorized step (TASK-002, default selected). This mirrors the current flagged/clean applicant pattern. Does this approach work for you?

