## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Delete the old `tokenflow.db` and start the server — verify schema creates cleanly
2. Start a "normal" workflow via the UI — verify all 3 steps (READ_OBJECT → CALL_INTERNAL_API → WRITE_OBJECT) complete with burned tokens
3. Start a "malicious" workflow — verify step 3 attempt to READ_REPO triggers security violation, flags token, halts execution
4. Kill switch — verify all tokens are revoked for a running workflow
5. Token chain integrity — verify parent chain linking is correct
6. WebSocket — verify real-time updates stream to frontend

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of the new dark futuristic UI with glassmorphism effects
- Verify the token chain DAG animates correctly
- Verify blocked step shows red indicator with security alert
- Verify credential vault shows new services
